TITLE: Manchin dodges on whether he wants Dems to control Congress, again declines to support Biden for 2024
SUMMARY: Appearing on multiple television programs Sunday morning, Sen. Joe Manchin refused to say whether he supported his fellow Democrats in upcoming elections.

TITLE: Biden connects through FaceTime with veterans exposed to burn pits: there is 'sacred obligation' to help them
SUMMARY: President Biden connected with veterans and their families on Saturday afternoon through FaceTime as they camp outside the Capitol urging the Senate to pass the PACT Act.

TITLE: Manchin admits 'mistake' saying past spending bill wouldn't cause inflation, hopes he isn't wrong again
SUMMARY: Sen. Joe Manchin, D-W.Va., is pushing for a new spending package, but admitted Sunday that he made a "mistake" in saying the American Rescue Plan would not cause inflation.

TITLE: Trump-backed Washington GOP House candidates to take on pro-impeachment Republicans
SUMMARY: Two Washington GOP House candidates, both endorsed by former President Trump, aim to defeat two incumbent Republicans who voted to impeach Trump last year.

TITLE: Democrats postpone decision on upending 2024 presidential primary calendar
SUMMARY: The Democratic National Committee is delaying until after November’s midterm elections a highly anticipated decision on changing the top of their 2024 presidential nominating calendar

TITLE: Strategists suggest recession could pose a threat to Democrats in midterm elections: 'People are hurting'
SUMMARY: Strategists from both sides of the aisle suggest Democrats could be at risk in the upcoming midterm elections due to the Biden administration's handling of the economy.

TITLE: Final countdown: Only 100 days left until the midterm elections
SUMMARY: Republicans and Democratic candidates make their final moves, with only 100 days left until the midterm election where many expect the GOP to retake the majority.

TITLE: Nancy Pelosi's Asia visit itinerary leaves out mention of possible stop in Taiwan
SUMMARY: House Speaker Nancy Pelosi's office said she is taking a trip to Asia and will visit at least four countries in the region, but Taiwan is not among her destinations.

TITLE: Arizona candidate aims to become state's first Hispanic congresswoman, says Dems take Latinos for granted
SUMMARY: A Republican candidate running in an Arizona primary would be the first Latina elected to office if she were to win November's midterm against Rep. Greg Stanton.

TITLE: Indiana Senate passes bill to ban most abortions
SUMMARY: A near-total abortion ban passed the GOP-controlled Indiana Senate during Saturday's special session by a 26 to 20 vote, and now heads to the House.

TITLE: Trump: Brittney Griner prisoner swap for 'Merchant of Death' doesn't 'seem like a very good trade'
SUMMARY: Former President Donald Trump said Saturday it "doesn't seem" like a good trade if the U.S. exchanges WNBA star Brittney Griner for a Russian arms dealer.

TITLE: Biden shares video after testing positive for COVID-19 again: 'I'm feeling fine'
SUMMARY: President Biden shared a video on social media after testing positive for COVID-19 again, stating that he's "feeling fine" and has "a little work to do."

TITLE: Biden 'played too loose' with CDC's mask guidance after negative COVID test, doctor says: 'Not a good look'
SUMMARY: After President Biden tested positive for COVID-19 in a "rebound infection," one doctor tells Fox News that Biden didn't set a good example for following CDC coronavirus guidelines.

TITLE: House 'assault weapons' ban approved by 18 vulnerable Democrats
SUMMARY: Several House Democrats considered to be vulnerable in the upcoming midterm elections voted in favor of an "assault weapons" ban on Friday.

TITLE: Biden tests positive for COVID in 'rebound' case, doctor says
SUMMARY: President Biden tested positive for a "rebound" case of COVID-19 on Saturday morning, according to the White House doctor in a letter.

TITLE: House Democrat overseeing Washington Commanders inquiry faces ethics complaint
SUMMARY: A government watchdog is demanding a probe into House Democrat Raja Krishnamoorthi, who is overseeing the congressional investigation into the NFL's Washington Commanders.

TITLE: Biden slams 'MAGA policies,' proposals to sunset Medicare, touts efforts to lower prescription drug costs
SUMMARY: President Biden on Saturday slammed Republican proposals and "MAGA policies" and touted his administration's efforts to give Medicare the "power" to negotiate lower drug prices.

TITLE: Video appears to show migrants led from bus to DC church, located steps away from U.S. Capitol
SUMMARY: Footage from video shot outside of St. Peter's Church in Washington, D.C., Friday appears to show migrants entering the church looking for assistance.

TITLE: Democratic Rep. Garcia lashes out at Twitter user with profanity, offensive term
SUMMARY: Illinois Democratic Rep. Chuy García lashed out at a Twitter user who criticized a gun control bill, using profanity and a term that many consider offensive.

TITLE: ELECTION SPOTLIGHT: Dr. Mehmet Oz and John Fetterman square off over Biden performance, economy
SUMMARY: Pennsylvania Senate candidates John Fetterman and Dr. Mehmet Oz both spoke to Fox News Digital about the economy, President Joe Biden and each other
